The Center for Disease Control and Prevention in Beijing has reported an outbreak in an imported unit in another province. The full text is as follows:

From 0000 to 2400 hours on February 26,2020, there were 10 confirmed cases in Beijing, all diagnosed after close contacts of the cases announced by Beijing on February 25, the outbreak was judged to be an imported unit-aggregated outbreak. The situation is explained as follows:

On February 23,2020, Beijing received a report of a suspected case of new coronary pneumonia. On February 24, at 4:00, the case was confirmed. All of his close contacts were put under medical isolation. As of February 26, a total of 10 cases had been confirmed among his close contacts, therefore, the outbreak involved a total of 11 confirmed cases, of which 10 were employees of a property management company that purchased services from an institution in Beijing and one was an employee of a catering company, all of the 11 cases were living in dormitories or working in property offices next to the dormitories of the units they served. All cases have been transferred to the municipal designated hospital isolation treatment, the current condition is stable. The outbreak has identified 178 close contacts, the city, district Centers for Disease Control and comprehensive disinfection of the unit, and the implementation of health surveillance and other comprehensive prevention and control measures.

The first case Sun Mou, has been in the unit engaged in cleaning services. He developed cough on February 18 and has been coming to work with illness. He felt chilly on the night of February 22, checked his temperature at 2:00 on February 23 and went to the medical institution at 8:00 on the same day. He was diagnosed as a suspected case. Tracing the source of infection of the first case, Sun Mou, revealed that the patient had close contact with a colleague from Hebei who returned to Beijing from Handan on February 3. He developed respiratory symptoms on February 7, he returned to his home in Handan, Hebei Province on February 9. Hebei CDC samples, found that the new coronavirus antibody positive, suggesting that had been infected with the new coronavirus.

More than cases have been reported in this institution recently. The reason was that the patients lived, ate and worked together with their colleagues in the collective dormitory for many days before and after the onset of the disease, as the source of infection from Handan, it was concluded that the epidemic was an imported work unit of the aggregation of the epidemic.

In this regard, we remind all units to strengthen logistics, cleaning, catering, security and other personnel management, accommodation density can not be too high, living places to air circulation, to avoid multi-people gathered for dinner or chat. All units should implement the main responsibility, strictly implement the requirement of 14-day medical observation at home or in concentrated isolation for those returning to Beijing from other places, and report to the community in a timely manner, so as to timely grasp the abnormal changes in the body such as fever and dry cough of the employees, and arrange to see a doctor as soon as possible. In the event of an outbreak, the CDC should take the initiative to carry out investigations, traceability, disinfection, isolation and other work.
